patthana16.74:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ajjhattikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.74:1.1_1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ajjhattikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …pe… anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ajjhattikaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko ca naanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha.
patthana16.74:2.1_0: Anidassanasappaṭighaṁ bāhiraṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nabāhiro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
